73 & thriving. The iconic @chefbabette sat down with us on The Sakara Life Podcast.

She emphasized the importance of forgiving those who have wronged you, her mantra for tackling life's obstacles, how she was introduced to a plant-based lifestyle and more with @danielleduboise and @whitneytingle.

Listen to The Sakara Life Podcast now at the link in bio or wherever you get your podcasts.
